jobInfo.postDescription:
岗位职责
1.Responsible for IDS(intrusion detection system) testing and error report							
2.Ability to create test cases according to specifications/user story	
3.Ability to understand test plan and test cases, and pull traces from each ECU with IDS scope(Gateway, connect ECU, etc.)
4.Performing the test cases with requested tools and systems (ODIS/idex/ADB/Canoe/WireShark/…)	 on test racks and vehicles
5.Analyzing IDS event reports on IDS backend with SQL commands 
6.Recording results in testing reports, creating bug reports in issues system and tracking the error status	
7.Supporting test environment(test rack and vehicle) setup	

任职要求	
1.Bachelor degree in Automotive/Computer Science/ Electrical Engineering/ Telecommunications	
2.3+ years in automotive industry, at least 2 years focus on ECU and EE network testing 
3.Good Knowledge in EE network and ECU communication protocols, such as CAN BUS, Some/IP, etc.
4.Good knowledge in testing tools/systems, such as Jira, Canoe, WireShark, ADB, etc. Experience of ODIS and iDEX will be plus	
5.Quick learner , good team work and good motivation				
Chinese & English (written and verbal) mandatory
jobInfo.address: 北京朝阳区霄云路33号大厦101
